&lt;p&gt;Sqlite is not multi-threaded so we can experience failures with concurrent writes. One way to prevent this issue from happening, is to append the &lt;code&gt;StreamingQueryListener&lt;/code&gt; events to append to a Python &lt;code&gt;queue.Queue()&lt;/code&gt; instead of directly to the database, so that all writes can be managed by a single thread.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>